 Geysers. </p>
<p>

<city wordnetid="108524735" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../189/901189.xml">
Antofagasta</link></city>
 is the largest city in Norte Grande. <curve wordnetid="113867641" confidence="0.8">
<arch wordnetid="113886133" confidence="0.8">
<line wordnetid="113863771" confidence="0.8">
