.</p>
<p>

The clear skies of Norte Chico and its infrastructure are ideal for Astronomical Tourism.</p>
<p>

<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../101/2051101.xml">
Elqui Valley</link> is a popular destination. Here, the dazzling green of the valley floor contrasts nicely with the barren brown slopes of the mountains that flank it.</p>

</sec>
<sec>
