</region>
 and Colchagua are some of the finest tours in Chile. <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../782/89782.xml">
Central Valley</link> is the <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../359/1504359.xml">
Huaso</link> Land by antonomasia. </p>
<p>

The surroundings of <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../572/51572.xml">
Santiago</link></village>
 include several attractions, such as the <link>
Cajón del Maipo</link>, <region wordnetid="108630985" confidence="0.8">
<administrative_district wordnetid="108491826" confidence="0.8">
<location wordnetid="100027167" confidence="0.8">
<municipality wordnetid="108626283" confidence="0.8">
<geographical_area wordnetid="108574314" confidence="0.8">
